revised_prompt: Create a high-resolution, ethereal sports analytics dashboard background. Display a deep cosmic purple-black gradient adorned with swirling golden nebulae. Showcase abstract data visualizations, presented as floating translucent 3D bar charts, pie charts, and line graphs in hues of gold and amber. Feature holographic hexagonal grid patterns and flowing data streams which resemble golden constellations. Incorporate silhouettes of a Black male and a Middle-Eastern female wrestler performing action poses, their forms subtly faded into the background mist. Floating numbers: 87, 342, 1249, 5.1, 106, 113, 120, 126, 132 should be distinctly visible in glowing gold. Detailed icons of trophies and medals should carry an ethereal glow. For ambience, include particle effects and light streams. The style should reflect a modern dashboard UI background, professional yet mystical sports visualization with a dark theme that carries luxury gold accents, cinematic lighting and 4K resolution. There should be no text or words, only numbers and visual elements.
